headline: ePlus: Strong Quarter, Stronger Case For A Re-Rating
summary: ePlus inc. beat estimates in Q1 FY26, refocusing on high-margin tech, AI, and cybersecurity, while launching dividends & buybacks. Click for more on PLUS earnings.
